1. *Desila* se oluja sinoć. (A storm *happened* last night.)
2. Prošle nedelje *se desilo* nešto jako čudno. (Something very strange *happened* last week.)
3. Da li se nekada *desilo* da se izgubiš u ovom delu grada? (Have you ever *happened* to get lost in this part of town?)
4. Kada se *desi* da imamo slobodnog vremena, volimo da putujemo. (When it *happens* that we have free time, we like to travel.)
5. *Desiće se* nešto neverovatno ovog vikenda! (Something incredible *will happen* this weekend!)
6. Nadam se da će se uskoro *desiti* nešto dobro. (I hope that something good *will happen* soon.)
7. *Desile* su se neke greške tokom procesa proizvodnje. (Some mistakes *occurred* during the production process.)
8. Kada se *bude desilo* da nađem novi posao, biću jako srećna. (When it *happens* that I find a new job, I will be very happy.)
9. Koliko često se *desi* da ljudi pobegnu odgovornosti? (How often *does it happen* that people shirk their responsibilities?)
10. Sve se *desilo* tako brzo da nismo uspeli da reagujemo. (Everything *happened* so quickly that we didn't manage to react.)